metadata.name: Yaygif #1
metadata.description: Yaygifs is a community-driven NFT project created by Yaypegs holders. We're driven to create timeless work by portraying an aesthetic that we can all uniquely feel identified with. Each Yaygif in the collection comes with a variety of traits, so you're sure to find one that speaks to you. With a collection size of 3,333, there's sure to be a Yaygif for everyone. Whether you're a fan of animation, art, or just love collecting unique items, Yaygifs is the perfect NFT project for you.
